{
  "video_id": "a4ZBzM3L6ws",
  "title": "A precise, three-word address for every place on earth | Chris Sheldrick",
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13810.0,
      "end_time": 15870.0,
      "text": "According to the UN,"
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15111.0,
      "end_time": 18357.0,
      "text": "billions of people still live without an address."
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 19154.0,
      "end_time": 21435.0,
      "text": "The economist Hernando de Soto said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 21459.0,
      "end_time": 22817.0,
      "text": "\"Without an address,"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22841.0,
      "end_time": 24743.0,
      "text": "you live outside the law."
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 24767.0,
      "end_time": 26384.0,
      "text": "You might as well not exist.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 27679.0,
      "end_time": 30830.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m here to tell you how my team and I are trying to change that."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 31986.0,
      "end_time": 35202.0,
      "text": "If you go to an online map and look at a favela in Brazil"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 35226.0,
      "end_time": 37500.0,
      "text": "or a township in South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 37740.0,
      "end_time": 40530.0,
      "text": "you&#39;ll see a few streets but a lot of empty space."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 40678.0,
      "end_time": 42821.0,
      "text": "But if you flip to satellite view,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42845.0,
      "end_time": 45958.0,
      "text": "there are thousands of people, homes and businesses"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45983.0,
      "end_time": 49190.0,
      "text": "in this vast, unmapped and unaddressed spaces."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49551.0,
      "end_time": 51411.0,
      "text": "In Ghana&#39;s capital, Accra,"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51435.0,
      "end_time": 55524.0,
      "text": "there are numbers and letters scrawled onto the sides of walls,"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 55548.0,
      "end_time": 58677.0,
      "text": "where they piloted address systems but not finished them."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 60163.0,
      "end_time": 63299.0,
      "text": "But these places, these unaddressed places,"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 63323.0,
      "end_time": 65319.0,
      "text": "hold huge economic potential."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 67201.0,
      "end_time": 69601.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s why the issue of addressing stuck with me."
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 70453.0,
      "end_time": 72505.0,
      "text": "I worked in the music business for 10 years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 72529.0,
      "end_time": 74907.0,
      "text": "and what you may not know about the music world"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74931.0,
      "end_time": 78344.0,
      "text": "is that every day, people struggle with the problems of addressing."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 78368.0,
      "end_time": 81196.0,
      "text": "So from the musicians who have to find the gigs"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 81221.0,
      "end_time": 83650.0,
      "text": "to the production companies who bring the equipment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 83674.0,
      "end_time": 85736.0,
      "text": "everyone somehow always gets lost."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 85760.0,
      "end_time": 87901.0,
      "text": "We even had to add someone to our schedules"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 87925.0,
      "end_time": 90744.0,
      "text": "who was the person you called when you thought you&#39;d arrived"
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90768.0,
      "end_time": 92152.0,
      "text": "but then realized you hadn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 92176.0,
      "end_time": 94499.0,
      "text": "And we had some pretty bad days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 94523.0,
      "end_time": 97708.0,
      "text": "like in Italy, where a truck driver unloaded all the equipment"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97732.0,
      "end_time": 100315.0,
      "text": "an hour north of Rome, not an hour south of Rome,"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100339.0,
      "end_time": 101548.0,
      "text": "and a slightly worse day"
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101572.0,
      "end_time": 103647.0,
      "text": "where a keyboard player called me and said,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103671.0,
      "end_time": 106585.0,
      "text": "\"Chris, don&#39;t panic, but we may have just sound-checked"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 106609.0,
      "end_time": 108172.0,
      "text": "at the wrong people&#39;s wedding.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 108196.0,
      "end_time": 109771.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 109795.0,
      "end_time": 112433.0,
      "text": "So not long after the fated Rome event,"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 112457.0,
      "end_time": 114565.0,
      "text": "I chatted this through with a friend of mine"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 114590.0,
      "end_time": 115754.0,
      "text": "who is a mathematician,"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 115778.0,
      "end_time": 118588.0,
      "text": "and we thought it was a problem we could do something about."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 118612.0,
      "end_time": 120949.0,
      "text": "We thought, well, we could make a new system,"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 120973.0,
      "end_time": 123450.0,
      "text": "but it shouldn&#39;t look like the old system."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 123628.0,
      "end_time": 125743.0,
      "text": "We agreed that addresses were bad."
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 126474.0,
      "end_time": 128500.0,
      "text": "We knew we wanted something very precise,"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 128524.0,
      "end_time": 130878.0,
      "text": "but GPS coordinates, latitude and longitude,"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 130901.99999999999,
      "end_time": 132386.0,
      "text": "were just too complicated."
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 133256.0,
      "end_time": 136990.0,
      "text": "So we divided the world into three-meter squares."
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 136583.0,
      "end_time": 140676.0,
      "text": "The world divides into around 57 trillion three-meter squares,"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 140700.0,
      "end_time": 142891.0,
      "text": "and we found that there are enough combinations"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 142915.0,
      "end_time": 144725.0,
      "text": "of three dictionary words"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 144749.0,
      "end_time": 148341.0,
      "text": "that we could name every three-meter square in the world uniquely"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 148365.0,
      "end_time": 149721.0,
      "text": "with just three words."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 150546.0,
      "end_time": 152117.0,
      "text": "We used 40,000 words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 152141.0,
      "end_time": 153733.0,
      "text": "so that&#39;s 40,000 cubed,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 153758.0,
      "end_time": 156991.0,
      "text": "64 trillion combinations of three words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 157150.0,
      "end_time": 160903.0,
      "text": "which is more than enough for the 57-trillion-odd three-meter squares,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 160927.0,
      "end_time": 162109.0,
      "text": "with a few spare."
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 163440.0,
      "end_time": 164993.0,
      "text": "So that&#39;s exactly what we did."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 165170.0,
      "end_time": 168910.0,
      "text": "We divided the world into three-meter squares,"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 168115.0,
      "end_time": 170956.0,
      "text": "gave each one a unique, three-word identifier --"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 170980.0,
      "end_time": 172712.0,
      "text": "what we call a three-word address."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 173385.0,
      "end_time": 176457.0,
      "text": "So for example, right here,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 176481.0,
      "end_time": 178676.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m standing at mustards.coupons.pinup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 178858.0,
      "end_time": 180800.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 180320.0,
      "end_time": 181883.0,
      "text": "but over here ..."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 182753.0,
      "end_time": 185701.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m standing at pinched. singularly.tutorial."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 189133.0,
      "end_time": 191104.0,
      "text": "But we haven&#39;t just done this in English."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 191128.0,
      "end_time": 194557.0,
      "text": "We thought it was essential that people should be able to use this system"
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 194581.0,
      "end_time": 195843.0,
      "text": "in their own language."
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 195867.0,
      "end_time": 198100.0,
      "text": "So far, we&#39;ve built it into 14 languages,"
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 198124.0,
      "end_time": 200567.0,
      "text": "including French, Swahili and Arabic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 200591.0,
      "end_time": 203423.0,
      "text": "and we&#39;re working on more now, like Xhosa, Zulu and Hindi."
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 205157.0,
      "end_time": 207400.0,
      "text": "But this idea can do a lot more"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 207280.0,
      "end_time": 209727.0,
      "text": "than just get my musicians to their gigs on time."
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 209752.0,
      "end_time": 213929.0,
      "text": "If the 75 percent of countries that struggle with reliable addressing"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 213953.0,
      "end_time": 215657.0,
      "text": "started using three-word addresses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 215681.0,
      "end_time": 218513.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a stack of far more important applications."
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 220330.0,
      "end_time": 222463.0,
      "text": "In Durban, South Africa,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 222487.0,
      "end_time": 224144.0,
      "text": "an NGO called Gateway Health"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 224168.0,
      "end_time": 227118.0,
      "text": "have distributed 11,000 three-word address signs"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 227142.0,
      "end_time": 228531.0,
      "text": "to their community,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 228555.0,
      "end_time": 230934.0,
      "text": "so the pregnant mothers, when they go into labor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 230958.0,
      "end_time": 232766.0,
      "text": "can call the emergency services"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 232790.0,
      "end_time": 235141.0,
      "text": "and tell them exactly where to pick them up from,"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 235165.0,
      "end_time": 238518.0,
      "text": "because otherwise, the ambulances have often taken hours to find them."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 238964.0,
      "end_time": 242241.0,
      "text": "In Mongolia, the National Post Service have adopted the system"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 242265.0,
      "end_time": 244702.0,
      "text": "and are now doing deliveries to many people&#39;s houses"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 244727.0,
      "end_time": 246128.0,
      "text": "for the first time."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 246152.0,
      "end_time": 249834.0,
      "text": "The UN are using it to geotag photos in disaster zones"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 249859.0,
      "end_time": 252531.0,
      "text": "so they can deliver aid to exactly the right place."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 252555.0,
      "end_time": 255225.0,
      "text": "Even Domino&#39;s Pizza are using it in the Caribbean,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 255249.0,
      "end_time": 257950.0,
      "text": "because they haven&#39;t been able to find customers&#39; homes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 257974.0,
      "end_time": 261168.0,
      "text": "but they really want to get their pizza to them while its still hot."
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 261728.0,
      "end_time": 264250.0,
      "text": "Shortly, you&#39;ll be able to get into a car,"
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 264274.0,
      "end_time": 266100.0,
      "text": "speak the three words,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 266340.0,
      "end_time": 268391.0,
      "text": "and the car will navigate you to that exact spot."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 269888.0,
      "end_time": 273412.0,
      "text": "In Africa, the continent has leapfrogged phone lines"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 273437.0,
      "end_time": 274830.0,
      "text": "to go to mobile phones,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 274854.0,
      "end_time": 278332.0,
      "text": "bypassed traditional banks to go straight to mobile payments."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 279298.0,
      "end_time": 283252.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re really proud that the post services of three African countries --"
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 283276.0,
      "end_time": 285872.0,
      "text": "Nigeria, Djibouti and CÃ´te d&#39;Ivoire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 285896.0,
      "end_time": 288548.0,
      "text": "have gone straight to adopting three-word addresses,"
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 288572.0,
      "end_time": 290645.0,
      "text": "which means that people in those countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 290669.0,
      "end_time": 293841.0,
      "text": "have a really simple way to explain where they live, today."
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 295167.0,
      "end_time": 298845.0,
      "text": "For me, poor addressing was an annoying frustration,"
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 298870.0,
      "end_time": 301374.0,
      "text": "but for billions of people,"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 301398.0,
      "end_time": 303811.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s a huge business inefficiency,"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 303835.0,
      "end_time": 306515.0,
      "text": "severely hampers their infrastructure growth,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 306540.0,
      "end_time": 307824.0,
      "text": "and can cost lives."
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 308837.0,
      "end_time": 310465.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re on a mission to change that,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 310489.0,
      "end_time": 311702.0,
      "text": "three words at a time."
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 311726.0,
      "end_time": 312877.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 312901.0,
      "end_time": 317418.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}